About the job
Job description
We are looking for an excellent Marketing manager to join our team in Brazil, and together build and develop our high-end fashion product. If you have a passion for the fashion world, experience in Marketing manager and want to join a dynamic and challenging environment, consider applying for this position.


Education level: University - Graduated

Business hours: Monday to Friday, from 8:10 a.m. to 6:00 p.m.

Ready to work

Activities

Desired responsibilities and experience:

Responsible for developing the company's Marketing strategy;
Manage all necessary actions to achieve the goals set out with the Board of Directors;
Implement Digital Marketing projects to create impact and brand visibility;
Monitor market indices and prepare price research;
Participate in building commercial strategies to open new business fronts;

Manage the organization of participants at fairs and events;
Manage the Marketing team;
Monitor and evaluate the recruitment of new suppliers in the area;
Develop strategic actions;
Take other actions related to the location.
The request
Bachelor's degree in Marketing or Communications;
Intermediate knowledge of Excel;
Experience in managing Marketing projects;
Have experience managing groups.

About the job
